<HL>
   Trouble Is Brewing
   Over Folgers' Use
   Of Salvadoran Beans
   ---
   Descendants of P&amp;G Founder
   Urge Changing Suppliers
   Until Unrest Ends in Area
   ----
   By Alecia Swasy
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
07/26/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
